{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Hi, my name is Marcin --"},{"time":3000,"text":"farmer, technologist."},{"time":5000,"text":"I was born in Poland, now in the U.S."},{"time":8000,"text":"I started a group called Open Source Ecology."},{"time":11000,"text":"We've identified the 50 most important machines"},{"time":13000,"text":"that we think it takes for modern life to exist --"},{"time":16000,"text":"things from tractors,"},{"time":18000,"text":"bread ovens, circuit makers."},{"time":20000,"text":"Then we set out to create"},{"time":22000,"text":"an open source, DIY, do it yourself version"},{"time":25000,"text":"that anyone can build and maintain"},{"time":27000,"text":"at a fraction of the cost."},{"time":29000,"text":"We call this the Global Village Construction Set."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31000,"text":"So let me tell you a story."},{"time":33000,"text":"So I finished my 20s"},{"time":35000,"text":"with a Ph.D. in fusion energy,"},{"time":37000,"text":"and I discovered I was useless."},{"time":40000,"text":"I had no practical skills."},{"time":42000,"text":"The world presented me with options,"},{"time":44000,"text":"and I took them."},{"time":46000,"text":"I guess you can call it the consumer lifestyle."},{"time":48000,"text":"So I started a farm in Missouri"},{"time":51000,"text":"and learned about the economics of farming."},{"time":54000,"text":"I bought a tractor -- then it broke."},{"time":57000,"text":"I paid to get it repaired --"},{"time":59000,"text":"then it broke again."},{"time":61000,"text":"Then pretty soon,"},{"time":63000,"text":"I was broke too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65000,"text":"I realized"},{"time":67000,"text":"that the truly appropriate, low-cost tools that I needed"},{"time":70000,"text":"to start a sustainable farm and settlement"},{"time":73000,"text":"just didn't exist yet."},{"time":75000,"text":"I needed tools that were robust, modular,"},{"time":78000,"text":"highly efficient and optimized,"},{"time":80000,"text":"low-cost,"},{"time":82000,"text":"made from local and recycled materials that would last a lifetime,"},{"time":85000,"text":"not designed for obsolescence."},{"time":87000,"text":"I found that I would have to build them myself."},{"time":90000,"text":"So I did just that."},{"time":93000,"text":"And I tested them."},{"time":96000,"text":"And I found that industrial productivity"},{"time":99000,"text":"can be achieved on a small scale."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"So then I published the 3D designs,"},{"time":105000,"text":"schematics,"},{"time":107000,"text":"instructional videos and budgets"},{"time":110000,"text":"on a wiki."},{"time":112000,"text":"Then contributors from all over the world"},{"time":114000,"text":"began showing up, prototyping new machines"},{"time":117000,"text":"during dedicated project visits."},{"time":119000,"text":"So far, we have prototyped eight of the 50 machines."},{"time":122000,"text":"And now the project"},{"time":124000,"text":"is beginning to grow on its own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127000,"text":"We know that open source has succeeded"},{"time":129000,"text":"with tools for managing knowledge and creativity."},{"time":132000,"text":"And the same is starting to happen with hardware too."},{"time":135000,"text":"We're focusing on hardware"},{"time":137000,"text":"because it is hardware that can change people's lives"},{"time":140000,"text":"in such tangible material ways."},{"time":143000,"text":"If we can lower the barriers to farming, building, manufacturing,"},{"time":146000,"text":"then we can unleash just massive amounts of human potential."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149000,"text":"That's not only in the developing world."},{"time":152000,"text":"Our tools are being made"},{"time":154000,"text":"for the American farmer, builder, entrepreneur, maker."},{"time":157000,"text":"We've seen lots of excitement from these people,"},{"time":159000,"text":"who can now start a construction business,"},{"time":161000,"text":"parts manufacturing,"},{"time":163000,"text":"organic CSA"},{"time":165000,"text":"or just selling power back to the grid."},{"time":169000,"text":"Our goal is a repository of published designs"},{"time":171000,"text":"so clear, so complete,"},{"time":173000,"text":"that a single burned DVD"},{"time":175000,"text":"is effectively a civilization starter kit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181000,"text":"I've planted a hundred trees in a day."},{"time":184000,"text":"I've pressed 5,000 bricks in one day"},{"time":187000,"text":"from the dirt beneath my feet"},{"time":191000,"text":"and built a tractor in six days."},{"time":194000,"text":"From what I've seen, this is only the beginning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197000,"text":"If this idea is truly sound,"},{"time":200000,"text":"then the implications are significant."},{"time":203000,"text":"A greater distribution of the means of production,"},{"time":206000,"text":"environmentally sound supply chains,"},{"time":209000,"text":"and a newly relevant DIY maker culture"},{"time":213000,"text":"can hope to transcend"},{"time":215000,"text":"artificial scarcity."},{"time":218000,"text":"We're exploring the limits"},{"time":220000,"text":"of what we all can do to make a better world"},{"time":223000,"text":"with open hardware technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":227000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}